    SHH2 I 2 Bright A_Light1
    SHH2 J 2 Bright A_Light2
    Goto LightDone
  BalancedFlash:
    SHO2 I 4 Bright A_Light1
    SHO2 J 3 Bright A_Light2
    Goto LightDone
  Spawn:
